<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>About OnTrack</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    html, body {
      height: auto !important;
      min-height: 100% !important;
      overflow-y: auto !important;
    }

    body {
      background-color: #000000;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
      overflow-y: auto;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .container {
      min-height: 100%;
    }

    .contact-title {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0.5rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    }

    .contact-title .highlight {
      color: #ffd700;
    }


    .form-group-wrapper {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .form-label {
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .form-control {
      background-color: #1a1a1a;
      border: 1px solid #333333;
      color: #ffffff;
      padding: 0.5rem;
    }

    .form-control::placeholder {
      color: #808080;
    }

    .form-control:focus {
      background-color: #222222;
      border-color: #ffd700;
      color: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 0.25rem rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.15);
    }

    .btn-send {
      background-color: #ffffff;
      color: #000000;
      border: 2px solid #ffffff;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      padding: 0.5rem 1.5rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .btn-send:hover {
      background-color: #ffd700;
      border-color: #ffd700;
      color: #000000;
    }

    .contact-box {
      padding: 1rem 0;
      text-align: center;
    }


    .contact-info p {
      margin: 0.5rem 0;
      color: #cccccc;
    }

    .contact-info .highlight {
      color: #ffd700;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="contact-box">
      <h1 class="contact-title">
        What is <span class="highlight">OnTrack</span>?
      </h1>
      <p class="lead px-4">
        OnTrack is a web application designed to help students track their academic progress and ensure they are meeting all degree requirements.
      </p>
      <h1 class="contact-title">
        Who built <span class="highlight">OnTrack</span>?
      </h1>
      <p class="lead px-4">
        Picture of each team member with their name and role in the project.
      </p>
      <p class="lead px-4">
        All Waterloo students hoping to make a difference in the lives of their peers.
      </p>

    </div>
  </div>

  <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>